    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-05-21</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-06-20T17:53:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Pre-Disaster Mitigation Act of 2008 - Amends the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act to: (1) increase the amount guaranteed to each state under the pre-disaster mitigation program; (2) require other financial assistance under the program to be awarded on a competitive basis; and (3) authorize appropriations for the program through FY2011. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
